{"tid":2464112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★葉劉：Burberry是她十分喜歡的品牌之一，毋須銷毀","createTime":"2021-03-27T08:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T10:12:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6c840d863ca3e318dc959ae5c0c3d5918468ce5c","tid":2464112,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:10:28.000Z","msg":"葉劉今早（27 日）出席電台節目後表示，認為不需要特意去破壞一些現有的產品，強調她的主要目的是希望品牌可收回聲明及道歉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n葉劉昨日指，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>Burberry是她十分喜歡的品牌之一</strong></span>，特別是其經典款羊毛頸巾，認為產品既美觀又保暖，但是基於該品牌對新疆作出失實及無理指控，因此決定即時停買及停用其產品，直至品牌道歉或撒回指控為止。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/604869/%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E6%A3%89%E8%8A%B1-%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%E7%A8%B1%E6%AF%8B%E9%A0%88%E9%8A%B7%E6%AF%80burberry%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81-%E5%81%9C%E7%94%A8%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F604869%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2596%2586%25E6%25A3%2589%25E8%258A%25B1-%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25AF%258B%25E9%25A0%2588%25E9%258A%25B7%25E6%25AF%2580burberry%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%2593%2581-%25E5%2581%259C%25E7%2594%25A8%25E7%259B%25AE%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25B8%258C%25E6%259C%259B%25E5%2593%2581%25E7%2589%258C%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%25AD%2589&d=jrWVSpMJYTM9%2F%2BTkK0Hr3xTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=33ac34fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/604869/%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E6%A3%89%E8%8A%B1-%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%E7%A8%B1%E6%AF%8B%E9%A0%88%E9%8A%B7%E6%AF%80burberry%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81-%E5%81%9C%E7%94%A8%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89</a>"},{"pid":"6bb7ec7485abbf16653cda6ae3cb0da8293500f1","tid":2464112,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" clas